profile_process_video::text_card_0::text: Adeemsicha yeroo ibsitutti qophii waan addaddaa argachuukee mirkaneeffadhu. Tokko tokka bal'isuun, dhiyeessuun fi giddu galeessaan waraabuudhaan. Qaamichi goodaayyaa hunduma keessa jiraachuun dirqama miti.
profile_process_video::title: Adeemsa Barreeffama Dhuunfaa
profile_process_video::clip_card_1::goal: Jalqaba adeemsichaa yookaan jalqaba tarkaanfii adeemsichaa agarsiisi.
profile_process_video::clip_card_8::goal: Taatichi yeroo inni adeemsicha xumuraa jirutti qabadhu. Sochiin mul'achuun ni bareecha.
profile_process_video::clip_card_5::goal: Adeemsicha keessatti tarkaanfii barbaachisaa itti aanu agarsiisi.
profile_process_video::clip_card_7::goal: Yoo seenaankee waa'ee waan qaamichi hordoftoof yookaan namoota ilaalanii godhu ta'e, deebii gochaa isaanii qabachuukee mirkaneeffadhu.
profile_process_video::clip_card_0::goal: Yeroo taatichi adeemsichaaf qophaa'u agarsiisi. Akkamitti qophaa'u?
profile_process_video::clip_card_4::goal: Tarkaanfii adeemsichaa barbaachisaa itti aanu agarsiisi.
